text: Ishmekeyevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Urazovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 251 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 37 km from Uchaly, 9 km from Urazovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Ishmekeyevo
